Description: CaramOS over-the-air update helper
 Provides a CaramOS-specific OTA update command, daily update check,
 desktop notifier, state tracking, logs, and best-effort rollback support.
 .
 Users only need to run: sudo caramos-ota
 .
 Features:
  - CLI-based update check, install, status, repair, and rollback
  - Daily automatic check via systemd timer
  - Desktop notification with GTK3 dialog (Vietnamese)
  - Privilege escalation through pkexec/polkit
  - Transaction logging and best-effort rollback
